==========================
XCL's TScintilla Component
==========================

===============
 Linux
=======

To compile the TScitilla component you need to:

1- Download Scintilla (http://www.scintilla.org/)
2- Change "scintilla/gtk/makefile" as is described at the end of this file
3- Compile it (type "make" in "scintilla/gtk" directory)
4- as root copy libscintilla.so to /usr/local/lib
5- Copy "scintilla/include/Scintilla.iface" to here
6- Type "make" here

===============
Windows
=======

The idea is the same as for linux... I belive you can do it!

I think you will need need to change the $LINKLIB directive in scintilla.tmpl

If you manage to compile it in windows please tell me: judison@gmail.com

===============

modifications to scintilla/gtk/makefile

# after COMPLIB=../bin/scintilla.a add:
SHAREDLIB=../bin/libscintilla.so

# chage all: $(COMPLIB) to:
all: $(COMPLIB) $(SHAREDLIB)

#aftec "$(COMPLIB)" rule add:

$(SHAREDLIB): DocumentAccessor.o WindowAccessor.o KeyWords.o StyleContext.o Document.o CallTip.o \
	ScintillaBase.o ContractionState.o Editor.o ExternalLexer.o PropSet.o PlatGTK.o \
	KeyMap.o LineMarker.o ScintillaGTK.o CellBuffer.o ViewStyle.o \
	RESearch.o Style.o Indicator.o AutoComplete.o UniConversion.o XPM.o \
	$(MARSHALLER) $(LEXOBJS)
	$(CC) -shared `$(CONFIGFLAGS)` $(CXXFLAGS) -o $@ $^
